Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I was little, \NI've seen strange things every now and then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My my, we didn't catch a thing today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go pick some akebi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.76,0:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see a human child just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The grandchild of Natsume Reiko,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.68,0:02:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the one with the Book of Friends, {\i1}should{\i0} have run this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie to me and I'll eat you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he run?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked yummy too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A human child.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.96,0:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The things I see are probably \Nwhat people would call demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My grandmother left me The Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.11,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was born with great mystical powers
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and challenged every demon she met to a battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she defeated them, she would force \Nthe demons to write their names in it,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}binding them as servant and master.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.08,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}The Book of Friends is a set of contracts. \NCall the names within and their owners cannot disobey.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I got it, I've spent \Nmy days running from demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to catch my breath before I go in.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacup?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come out from there!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go hiding under people's houses!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Touko{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping took longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.42,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I thought I saw a rat, \Nbut it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a cat, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're covered in dirt...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Oh right, we're having beef hot pot tonight, Takashi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was close.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.90,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to be careful not to do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.16,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there really was a rat, we need to buy rat traps.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think I mistook something else for a rat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was one of the neighbor's puppies.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi{**-kun}, would you like some more?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost my parents when I was young,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.34,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my relatives passed me around \Nuntil the Fujiwaras finally took me in.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This home is very dear to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.85,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a Shadow Teacup.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been living underneath the house \Nfor about two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been there two weeks?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.61,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{*}Master{*Sensei}, you're supposed to be guarding the house!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I won!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get me another, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When an exceptionally well-made teacup \Nis broken and thrown away,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.96,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it sometimes absorbs the power of the Earth \Nand becomes a spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.92,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it takes up residence under \Nold houses just to be near people.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can be near people?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that sometimes, \Nwhen a disaster is about to strike,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll run around the house to warn everyone,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.51,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes, on a whim, \Nit'll sacrifice itself to prevent it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not dangerous?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it gets bored, it'll leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not a guard,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here because you promised to hand \Nover the Book of Friends when you die,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.24,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm protecting you from other spirits \Nthat try to get it before me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Natsume{*Natsume-sama}, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to ask for my name back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I inherited the Book of Friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.92,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've returned the names of the demons within it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.43,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I bring up an image \Nof them in my mind, and concentrate.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That which shields me, reveal thy name.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.60,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}To release their names, you need the saliva and breath \Nof someone of the same bloodline as Reiko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I return a name, I get really tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes another page out of the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They come without warning, \Nand then they leave the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.22,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4687,5730,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}Will I ever become strong enough \Nto not have my life ruled by them?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sounds like footsteps.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear that sometimes, \Nwhen a disaster is about to strike,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it'll run around the house to warn everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's running around already!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.09,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.01,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, some kind of disaster \Nis about to happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally starting to have love problems?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just didn't get much sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Up late reading dirty mags again?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? What's going on with Natsume{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's no fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made some friends since I moved to this town.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.66,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My grandmother, Reiko{**-san}, \Napparently didn't have many human friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.67,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's probably why she picked fights \Nwith every demon she met.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my staff, my staff...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your staff is right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're so kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see me, can't you, boy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's a demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What incredible power you have, boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What perfect timing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see well, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.46,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help this old woman out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.00,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed a mirror from \Na very powerful spirit a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.01,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know its name, but the other demons feared it \Nbecause it brought terrible disasters.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.51,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with your power should be able to find it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.02,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see spirits, but you don't know \Nwhat happens when you refuse one?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.45,0:09:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get involved with a demon that brings disaster...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(2811,3352,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}If something were to happen to the Fujiwaras...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've taken a liking to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't help me,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll curse you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!{ends on scenechange to nyanko}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble. Some weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been cursed, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares lay a hand on my prey?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An old lady...{added stutter}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.95,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An old lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.20,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.62,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.62,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something the old lady said really bothered me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shadow Teacup is running...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because I brought disaster?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to bloom this year, either?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it withers away,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sad and have nothing to look forward to.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.73,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it that old spirit?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I came.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why?{stutter added}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd wait 'til tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've finally met somebody \Nwho could find that spirit,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a waste if you got away.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not a patient lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you not?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't come into this house!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that old lady somebody so powerful \Nthat even you couldn't get rid of her?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.83,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably a spirit \Nthat was worshiped and enshrined.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.79,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be all right, but someone less powerful \Nwould be cursed if they touched her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's that strong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.05,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, most gods like her are sick or weakened.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.68,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like she can barely see,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so go with her for a bit and just get it over with.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So someone less powerful can't even get close.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.56,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that why she's so glad she found \Na human who can see demons?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A god who can't approach spirits or humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reiko{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice, did I?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A flower?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it might be a bit showy, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It does smell nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... it does, it does.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can meet it in the forest this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.48,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop calling me "boy".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she doesn't spend a lot of time with demons,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she wouldn't know about the Book of Friends \Nor the Natsume family.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty easy place to get lost in.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I met that spirit right over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This demon that could bring disaster...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what was he like?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.76,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't really see it, but it was pretty small.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Small...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.60,0:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If worst comes to worst, \N{*}Master{*Sensei} and I might be able to take him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't she say she borrowed a mirror from it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though it was that dangerous?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... so that's what bothered me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have many friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.70,0:13:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an old cherry tree near here,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was possessed by a stubborn evil spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An old tree... so that's what that dream was.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.79,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So it started to wither, \Nand to get rid of it I needed a mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.01,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for a mirror, \Nand then I found somebody holding one.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would steal it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was defeated and knocked away.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much of a god, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, when I begged for the mirror, \Nthat spirit gave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But everybody was afraid of it...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He must not be so bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.70,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other spirits always \Nkept their distance out of fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That spirit said the same thing,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that disaster followed everywhere it went.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It said it wasn't very fond of humans, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.80,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the mirror, but I couldn't get rid of the spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to give it back,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.35,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but that spirit said that it didn't like looking \Nin the mirror, and refused to take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.47,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I started to come \Nand see it every once in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked really close,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see that they had a scar here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.86,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirits were so scared of it, \Nand yet the wound came from a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.32,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That spirit was kind of cute. \NWhen I invited it to my home, it looked at my shrine...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and, for some reason, seemed kind of disappointed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.59,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told that spirit why I'd wanted the mirror, \Nit got rid of the spirit in the tree for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.34,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower is from that tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.89,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But why, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.85,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like that spirit,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you look kind of like it, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.19,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me look at that mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a while now, the Book of Friends has felt warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, is the spirit you're looking for—{added em dash}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally found you,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume of the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you won't get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one from before!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My left shoulder...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!{starts on blue dragon}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being such a wimp!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good... your shoulder's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it ate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it doesn't seem to be broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought that lump of fur \Nwas supposed to be your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of that thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this kid that needs to pay more attention!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to be more careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like it used to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{fade from black if you want}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.15,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't care if he loses an arm or a leg or two \Nas long as the Book of Friends is safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Friends is safe, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,your name is in the Book of Friends, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.29,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NI did write my name in something.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.54,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, that spirit \Nstopped coming for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She was probably human.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother, Natsume Reiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That which shields me, reveal thy name.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I return your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take it,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aokuchinashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How infuriating.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.37,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers of that tree were my one pleasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had a mirror...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she brings disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's said to be more terrible than a demon god.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.31,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We should stay away.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lets.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The one who smells like a child of man...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take it anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've failed.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My staff... my staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your staff is here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give me your mirror?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The one friend I have needs a mirror!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They sell mirrors at the store up the road.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you lend it to me for just a little while? Please?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can look at my wound, \Nbut I don't have any medicine for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let me see...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange person.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here again.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your mirror back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.09,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like looking in the mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.64,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here often, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.47,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go further away, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Much, much farther away.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To a place nobody knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to my home?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.66,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. It's almost withered away, \Nbut there's a tree with beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A shrine...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.59,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange \Nfor somebody to care about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a spirit, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have a match with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll do anything you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat me if you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.99,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I win, you'll write your name...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.28,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the match and wrote \Nmy name on a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.12,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She never did give me her name.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... so it's Reiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was Natsume Reiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.01,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Reiko is no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep that mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.69,0:20:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been a great help, grandson of Reiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down that path, \Nand you'll return to the land of men.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.07,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight down that path!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.37,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like how the old woman thought \Nthat Reiko{**-san} was a spirit,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reiko{**-san} thought she was human.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she thought she had a human friend,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she must have been so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(1227,1769,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}I thought it was strange...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.71,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if that's when she began to dislike demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume, look!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those flowers, they're the ones...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is the tree Reiko banished the spirit from.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy woman, for a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.82,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She got rid of the evil spirit from the tree \Nafter she learned that the old lady was a spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Touko{**-san}, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Takashi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a tea cup I've never seen before here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See, whose is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(23,315,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H02060E&)\t(5195,5737,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}...and sometimes, on a whim, \Nit'll sacrifice itself to prevent it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They come without warning,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and then they leave the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But once you meet them,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if nobody ever knows it,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.61,0:22:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that encounter will change your life for the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The village of Ukihara?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.59,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a legendary village that's not part of this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did they get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.47,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think the smell of baked squid and\N the sound of festival music brought them here?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.68,0:24:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to return.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.18,0:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, if possible.
